<a name="2"></a>
<h2>Inserting Recommendations in a Catalog Page</h2>

<p>Catalogs that provide the urls of both their catalog pages and the resource pages they describe receive links to both pages when they request recommendations.</p>
<pre>
  &lt;script type="text/javascript" src="http://www.folksemantic.com/recommendations.pjs?u=http://www.oercommons.org/courses/5-068-physical-methods-in-inorganic-chemistry-spring-2005"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
</pre>

<p>Generates:</p>

<div class="example">
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/recommendations.pjs?u=http://www.oercommons.org/courses/5-068-physical-methods-in-inorganic-chemistry-spring-2005"></script>
</div>

<p><b><a href="/recommendations.pjs?u=http://www.oercommons.org/courses/5-068-physical-methods-in-inorganic-chemistry-spring-2005">See the Javascript</a></b></p>

