<a name="3"></a>
<h2>Snippet Options</h2>


<dt><b>limit</b></dt>  
<dd>
  Number of items to retrieve. 5 is the default when requesting XML and using the HTML scriptlet. 20 is the maximum that is ever returned.
  <a href="/recommendations?limit=3&details=true&u=http://openlearn.open.ac.uk/course/view.php?name=B821_1">Example</a>
</dd>

<dt><b>title</b></dt>  
<dd>
  Specify <b>true</b> to request a title be displayed above the list of recommendations.
</dd>

<dt><b>more_link</b></dt>  
<dd>
  Specify <b>true</b> to request a link to more links be displayed below the list of recommendations.
</dd>

<dt><b>direct_link_text</b></dt>  
<dd>
  Use to specify the anchor text for [direct link] links in catalog pages.
</dd>

<dt><b>details</b></dt>  
<dd>
  Specify <b>true</b> to request that all available details be displayed.
</dd>

<dt><b>omit_feeds</b></dt>  
<dd>
  Specify a comma delimited list of <a href="/collections">collections</a> to not include in the returned recommendations. 
</dd>

<p>For example:</p>

<p class="code">
  &lt;script type="text/javascript" src="http://www.folksemantic.com/recommendations.pjs?<br/>details=true&limit=12&title=true&more_link=true&direct_link_text=[go]<br/>&u=http://www.oercommons.org/courses/molecular-spectra-and-molecular-structure-spring-1996"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
</p>

<p>Generates:</p>

<div class="example">
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/recommendations.pjs?details=true&limit=12&title=true&more_link=true&direct_link_text=[go]&u=http://www.oercommons.org/courses/molecular-spectra-and-molecular-structure-spring-1996"></script>
</div>

<p><b><a href="/recommendations.pjs?details=true&limit=12&title=true&more_link=true&direct_link_text=[go]&u=http://www.oercommons.org/courses/molecular-spectra-and-molecular-structure-spring-1996">See the Javascript</a></b></p>

